    "If any issues occur within the app please report it via the GitHub repository. When submitting an issue, make sure to submit detailed information." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Falls ein Fehler auftritt mit der App, melde dies bitte über das GitHub-Repositorium. Beim einreichen von einem Fehler, stelle sicher detaillierte Informationen anzugeben."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "If any issues occur within the app please report it via the GitHub repository. When submitting an issue, make sure to submit detailed information."
          }
        },
        "pl" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Jeśli wystąpią jakiekolwiek problemy w aplikacji, zgłoś je za pośrednictwem repozytorium GitHub. Podczas zgłaszania problemu upewnij się, że podajesz szczegółowe informacje."
          }
        },
        "vi" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Nếu có bất kỳ vấn đề nào xảy ra trong ứng dụng, vui lòng báo lỗi qua kho lưu trữ GitHub. Khi báo lỗi, hãy đảm bảo gửi thông tin chi tiết."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Se riscontri qualche problema con l'app per favore segnalalo sulla repository di GitHub. Quando invii il problema, assicurati di inviare informazioni dettagliate."
          }
        }
      }
    },
