    "Server (Recommended):\\nUses a locally hosted server to install applications.\\n\\nIDevice (advanced):\\nUses a VPN and a pairing file. Writes to AFC and manually calls installd, while monitoring install progress by using a callback\\nAdvantage: It is very reliable, does not need SSL certificates or a externally hosted server. Rather, works similarly to a computer." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Server (Recommended):\\nUses a locally hosted server to install applications.\\n\\nIDevice (advanced):\\nUses a VPN and a pairing file. Writes to AFC and manually calls installd, while monitoring install progress by using a callback\\nAdvantage: It is very reliable, does not need SSL certificates or a externally hosted server. Rather, works similarly to a computer."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Server (Consigliato):Utilizza un server ospitato localmente e itms-services:// per installare le applicazioni.iDevice (Avanzato):Utilizza una VPN e un file di abbinamento. Scrive tramite AFC e richiama manualmente installd, monitorando l’avanzamento dell’installazione tramite una callback.Vantaggi:È molto affidabile, non richiede certificati SSL né un server ospitato esternamente. Funziona in modo simile a un computer."
          }
        }
      }
    },
